Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.islands

Class Island

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.islands.Island
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseIsland, SuperIsland
public abstract class Island extends Object implements Serializable
Island class is an abstract specification to be extended either with a BaseIsland or a SuperIsland.
